Text: Försökte att lägga upp rar filerna men fick bara error. så jag packade upp filen, Hoppas att ingen blir besviken.

Picture quality on this release is decent. Coming in with a resolution of 544×304, picture is a little more blurry compared to other DVD screener rips and there is a ?for screener purposes only? stamp which appears in some parts of the film. The 131 kbps VBR audio sounds decent and audible. Nice release here from VillageidiotS; this movie looks interesting.
